PN,40201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FThe public will be able to watch
OL,7,Fpenguin health checks and frog X-rays
OL,8,Fin a new #20 million wildlife health
OL,9,Fcentre, the Zoological Society of
OL,10,FLondon has said as it marks its 200th
OL,11,Fanniversary.
OL,13,FThe new facility at ZSL London Zoo,
OL,14,Fwill deliver care for zoo animals,
OL,15,Fmonitor emerging diseases in the wild
OL,16,Fand undertake conservation work such
OL,17,Fas health-checking wildlife including
OL,18,Fhazel dormice before releases into the
OL,19,Fwild.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FThe centre - funded by an anonymous
OL,7,Fdonation that is the biggest in the
OL,8,Fconservation charity's 200-year
OL,9,Fhistory - will bring veterinary
OL,10,Fscience to the public with the UK's
OL,11,Ffirst vet hospital viewing gallery for
OL,12,Fvisitors.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FPeople will be able to watch
OL,7,Fveterinary care taking place, such as
OL,8,FX-raying mountain chicken frogs as
OL,9,Fpart of health checks for London Zoo's
OL,10,Fpopulation of the critically
OL,11,Fendangered amphibians, which have been
OL,12,Fdriven to the brink of extinction in
OL,13,Ftheir wild Caribbean home by the
OL,14,Fdevastating chytrid fungus.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FVisitors will also see science
OL,7,Fresearch such as porpoise and dolphin
OL,8,Fautopsies following strandings around
OL,9,Fthe coast of England and Wales, and
OL,10,Fdisease surveillance including the pre-
OL,11,Frelease checks done on hazel dormice
OL,12,Fbefore they are released in
OL,13,Freintroduction projects in woods
OL,14,Faround the country.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FThe centre will also expand the
OL,7,Fexisting work to teach wildlife vets
OL,8,Fand conservation scientists with
OL,9,Fpostgraduate training, specialist
OL,10,Ftraining and field-based training in
OL,11,Fbiodiversity hotspots, the charity
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FKathryn England, ZSL chief executive,
OL,7,Fsaid: "For 200 years, ZSL has been
OL,8,Fcommitted to growing our understanding
OL,9,Fof wildlife and taking people on that
OL,10,Fjourney with us; from opening the
OL,11,Fworld's first scientific zoo, to
OL,12,Flaunching the Institute of Zoology,
OL,13,Fand establishing global conservation
OL,14,Fprojects.
OL,16,F"In those two centuries we have
OL,17,Fevolved from studying wildlife, to
OL,18,Fconserving it, to fighting for it."
OL,26,@oD@GOUxD@AOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FThe team at ZSL said it had a long
OL,7,Fhistory of veterinary care, from
OL,8,Femploying the first visiting vet for
OL,9,Fthe zoo in 1829 who saw the animals
OL,10,Ftwice a week, to the appointment of
OL,11,FBritain's first dedicated zoo vet in
OL,12,F1959 and the creation of Europe's
OL,13,Ffirst purpose-built zoo vet hospital
OL,14,Fstill in use today at London Zoo.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FThe charity also works studying
OL,7,Fwildlife diseases and their spread,
OL,8,Ffrom bovine TB to how the multiple
OL,9,Fviruses carried by bats can spill over
OL,10,Finto humans, and says the new centre
OL,11,Fwill embody the "one health" approach
OL,12,Fthat the health of animals, humans and
OL,13,Fecosystems are fundamentally connected.
OL,26,@sD@QOUsD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FMs England added: "We established the
OL,7,Ffoundations of modern zoo veterinary
OL,8,Fcare, have advanced conservation
OL,9,Fscience on a global scale and been at
OL,10,Fthe vanguard of public engagement with
OL,11,Fwildlife; our history has shaped how
OL,12,Fwildlife is studied, treated and
OL,13,Fprotected.
OL,15,F"Now, that legacy becomes a platform
OL,16,Ffor action."
OL,26,@nD@SOUwD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/15
