PN,40210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FThe move is announced as ZSL, which
OL,7,Fwas founded in 1826 and opened the
OL,8,Fworld's first scientific zoo, in
OL,9,FRegent's Park in 1828, celebrates its
OL,10,F200th anniversary.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/15
