FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FZSL's head of wildlife health
OL,7,Fservices, Dr Amanda Guthrie, told the
OL,8,FPress Association the new centre would
OL,9,Fbe a "state-of-the-art facility" that
OL,10,Fwould provide more space for the
OL,11,Fveterinary team and equipment,
OL,12,Fpotentially housing new technology
OL,13,Fsuch as a CT scanner and new post-
OL,14,Fmortem areas.
OL,26,@qD@FOUqD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FUnder the plans, which are at an early
OL,7,Fstage with the exact site of the new
OL,8,Ffacility still being discussed, it
OL,9,Fwill also have audio-visual equipment
OL,10,Fto allow teaching for wildlife vets
OL,11,Fand conservationists remotely around
OL,12,Fthe world.
OL,14,F"This facility will allow us to do
OL,15,Fmore teaching and research and
OL,16,Fcollaboration, and provide even better
OL,17,Fcare for the animals," Dr Guthrie said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,F"But for us, most importantly, we want
OL,7,Fvisitors to get to see the work we do,
OL,8,Fwe want to be transparent, we want
OL,9,Fpeople to really see the excellent
OL,10,Fcare we provide, but then also for
OL,11,Fpeople to understand how important
OL,12,Fwildlife health is in the conservation
OL,13,Fspace."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/15
