OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777464668
OL,3,CPublic able to view vets in action at
OL,4,CZSL's planned wildlife health centre
OL,6,FAnd she said: "We're really excited
OL,7,Ffor the public to get to see the work
OL,8,Fwe do and understand the high degree
OL,9,Fof animal welfare we aspire to every
OL,10,Fsingle day in the exemplary care that
OL,11,Fthese animals receive, and to be
OL,12,Finspired to consider careers in
OL,13,Fwildlife health and wildlife
OL,14,Fconservation."
OL,26,@nD@OOUvD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/15
